0,"totalTokens":134217,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"feishu","lastTo":"user:ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b","lastAccountId":"default","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/e8f65274-c7af-4fd4-b471-8c1235ec5149.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"知识库已同步更新。现在让我汇报学习成果。"},{"type":"text","text":"已完成学习并同步到本地+知识库。\n\n**学习总结：**\n\n从 awesome-openclaw-tutorial 学到了5个可落地的能力提升方向：\n\n| 能力 | 应用场景 | 优先级 |\n|------|----------|--------|\n| **多Agent分工** | 日报审核、项目跟进、行业研究、客服答疑分由不同agent处理 | ⭐⭐⭐ |\n| **Skills扩展** | 探索1715个企业级skills，寻找适合道简垂直领域的 | ⭐⭐ |\n| **自动化工作流** | 定时推送行业政策、竞品动态监控、项目进度提醒 | ⭐⭐⭐ |\n| **文件智能管理** | 道简项目文档自动归类整理 | ⭐⭐ |\n| **知识库进阶** | 自动归档行业报告、政策文件 | ⭐⭐ |\n\n**后续计划：**\n- 探索多Agent分工可能性\n- 研究Skills生态中适合To B科技服务的技能\n- 优化现有工作流程的自动化程度\n\n是否需要我现在就某个方向深入研究？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774590956266},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-27 14:04:27 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | 姚霖 (ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b) [msg:om_x100b535590666cb4c49491851e2e4b6, reply_to:om_x100b5355f1950c8cb3b3e27c5d9941c]\n\n\n\n\n全部研究"}],"timestamp":1774591469254,"senderLabel":"姚霖 (ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b)"}]},{"key":"agent:main:cron:d0fd6a2f-f302-4007-874b-0df8159f7a91","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: 每日复盘-教训反思","displayName":"Cron: 每日复盘-教训反思","updatedAt":1774584000011,"sessionId":"10c2e21c-96ad-48f1-a134-e55ea960c32e","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":58626,"systemSent":true,"transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/10c2e21c-96ad-48f1-a134-e55ea960c32e.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:d0fd6a2f-f302-4007-874b-0df8159f7a91 每日复盘-教训反思] 每日复盘任务：\n\n1. 回顾今天姚总对我的所有批评、反馈和教训\n2. 读取 memory/lessons.md 和 memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md（今天和昨天）\n3. 提炼出姚总批评的核心问题和教训\n4. 深度反思：为什么会犯错？根因是什么？\n5. 制定具体措施确保不再犯同类