{"type":"message","id":"3e21e990","parentId":"2d44a2c5","timestamp":"2026-03-28T02:19:10.156Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the sessions, I can see:\n\n1. The most recent user activity is from 姚霖 (the user) in the feishu direct session: `agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b` with timestamp 1774591468261 (which is March 27, 2026 at 14:04:27 based on the system message)\n\n2. The current time is March 28, 2026 at 10:18 AM\n\nSo the last user message was at March 27, 14:04 (2:04 PM), which is about 20 hours ago (not within the last 5 minutes).\n\nThe cron task session `agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978` was updated at 1774664329868 (which is about now), but that's this cron job's own session, not a user conversation.\n\nSo there is NO active user conversation in the last 5 minutes. I should execute the self-learning task.\n\nLet me proceed with:\n1. Search for latest news on enterprise digital transformation, intelligent security, network system integration, IT operations services\n2. Organize 3-5 key pieces of information\n3. Save to /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md","thinkingSignature":"0d29af41a3ff67d09e6d12257b752c9b26079b1e2af76d0a7e2462d2d6ec759f"},{"type":"text","text":"\n检测到当前无活跃用户对话（最近一次用户消息为2026-03-27 14:04，距今约20小时前）。开始执行自主学习任务。\n\n先搜索行业最新动态：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_06sg1mhbrq5v_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":7919,"output":383,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52283,"cost":{"input":0.0023756999999999997,"output":0.0004596,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00415473}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774664339189}}
{"type":"message","id":"8f86601c","parentId":"3e21e990","timestamp":"2026-03-28T02:19:10.164Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_06sg1mhbrq5v_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774664350161}}
{"type":"message","id":"5edf6aa2","parentId":"8f86601c","timestamp":"2026-03-28T02:19:17.131Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me search for relevant industry news for 道简网络. The company focuses on:\n- 企业数字化转型 (Enterprise digital transformation)\n- 智能安防 (Intelligent security/surveillance)\n- 网络系统集成 (Network system integration)\n- IT全周期运维服务 (Full-cycle IT operations services)\n\nLet me do multiple searches for these topics.","thinkingSignature":"d594f396cd711795a8fb8272116b9da8983462b286998d2e16f2ce26191db114"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_64ej2c3l8o2x_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026年最新政策趋势\" 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_64ej2c3l8o2x_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 弱电工程 市场动态 2026\" 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_64ej2c3l8o2x_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务行业发展趋势 2026\" 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":8817,"output":248,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53046,"cost":{"input":0.0026451,"output":0.00029759999999999997,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004262129999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774664350163}}
